<subSubSection pageId="64" pageNumber="772" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="64.[1476,2680,715,1220]" pageId="64" pageNumber="772">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1478,1834,1034,1063]" pageId="64" pageNumber="772">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Not yet assessed on The [UCN Red List. No information is available on population trends of or threats to the Mechuka Giant Flying Squirrel. More surveys and basic research on its distribution, population status, and natural history are needed to better understand threats and useful conservation action.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
